data.description: Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a single-level, three bedroom, two bathroom townhouse perfectly situated in the heart of South Beverly Estates. This home offers a blend of comfort and convenience, with highlights such as luxurious vinyl plank flooring in the dining and living areas, plush carpeting in the bedrooms and hallway, and a convenient pantry located in the hallway. The master suite boasts its own private bath for added luxury and comfort. Energy-efficient gas heating. Step outside to discover a fully fenced backyard and a spacious covered deck, ideal for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors. With an attached one-car garage completing the package, this home truly is a must-see!
